<td id="1B0AACA458105AF4E7996A7433CCE27F" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Obscurely denticulate being entire in appearance</td>
<td id="2EFADD8BDDDF71A8C36A3D11EA07D70E" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Seemingly entire immature but finely crenulate when mature</td>
</tr>
