<td id="BAB6589CEB7C3C3182C1E5B6DD3BD1AF" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Glabrous on both surfaces except for margin with scattered stellate hairs beneath</td>
<td id="5BECAEA2C21B0C884DC8155BACE4A268" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Glabrous above except sparsely hairy to glabrescent on midrib Beneath</td>
