<td id="4F3E754EC55D01021172F67B15690CD0" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Lateral veins 13-15 pairs, distinct above, prominent beneath, inter-secondary veins present in between</td>
<td id="A9DBD93768A86A3FF6EF6F78C434BB19" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" rowspan="1">Lateral veins 20-24, distinct and slightly prominent on both surfaces, brochidodromus with secondary veins looping and joining 0.2-0.5 mm in from the margin with distinct secondary loops</td>
</tr>
